episodes.title: Janette’s Take On…Mary Cosby: Cult Claims, Couture, & Chaos on The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City
episodes.description:
Mary Cosby is one of the most controversial figures in The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City — and she’s back in the spotlight. From cult allegations and explosive cast dynamics to unforgettable fashion moments and headline-making behavior, Mary Cosby continues to divide fans and fuel conversation.

In this Janette’s Take On…, I breaks down:

Why Mary Cosby remains one of the most polarizing Housewives
The power dynamics and discomfort surrounding her return
What Bravo gets right — and wrong — by keeping her in the spotlight
Whether controversy still equals compelling TV in today’s cultural climate
Bold, honest, and unapologetic — this is a take you won’t hear anywhere else.
